CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 2, 1958, pg. A4, reads: "Contest Finals - After a hard race in Baby Contest sponsored by the Conference Workers of Homewood AME Zion Church Sunday, young hopefuls hearing the contest finals are, seated, left to right: Edwin D. Moss, first prize winner; Lynn D. Walker, Michael J. Smith, second; Deleena I. Morten, third; Francine Dorsey, Shelia Brown, and Kathy Dean. Jerome Miller and Arthelbert Parker are standing in the foreground. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of five women and babies and children including Jerome Miller and Arthelbert Parker standing in front, and Edwin D. Moss, Lynn D. Walker, Michael J. Smith, Deleena I. Morten, Francine Dorsey, Shelia Brown, and Kathy Dean in background, for baby contest in Homewood AME Zion Church, another version
